graph

Class Graph<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • graph.Graph<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - Type of the keys
    V - Type of the vertices

    public class Graph<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
    An undirected, unweighted graph data structure, represented as a map of keys to vertices, with each vertex containing a list of adjacent vertices.
